high_descs: Head rotate and turn right to the sofa.
Pick the fruit from the sofa.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave.
Place the fruit inside the microwave.
Pick it back and turn left and turn right towards the fridge.
Place the fruit inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To place the fruit inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the fruit from the sofa.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the fruit into the microwave.
Then take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the fruit into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Placed the fruit into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and move right towards the sofa.
Pick the fruit from the sofa.
Turn right and move along the sofa, then head right towards the microwave.
Place the fruit in the microwave and pick it back after heating.
Turn right and head to the dining table, then walk along the table and head right towards the fridge.
Place the fruit in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the fruit in the fridge by heating it in the microwave oven.
